
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Milestone 1: Basic Charting
------------------------------------------------------------------------

    o   View chart of any stock

    o   Charts display price information, zoom, and resize

    o   Data acquisition complete; data is downloaded automatically and
        cached in database


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Milestone 2: Technical Analysis
------------------------------------------------------------------------

    o   Technical analysis library complete

    o   Charting can display selected technical analyses and buy/sell
        signals


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Milestone 3: Training and Evaluation of Prediction Profiles
------------------------------------------------------------------------

    o   Neural network implementation complete

    o   Neural networks persisted in database

    o   Trainer interface complete, including ability to select
        technical analyses

    o   Evaluator interface complete, including additional charting
        capabilities


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Milestone 4: Prediction Profile Searching
------------------------------------------------------------------------

    o   User can search through security listings based on prediction
        profiles.

    o   Includes interface for tabulating and browsing search results


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Milestone 5: Portfolio management
------------------------------------------------------------------------

    o   Data management system can keep track of security purchases and
        sales

    o   Evaluate actual trades with optimal strategies based on
        individual securities or indices


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Milestone 6: Temporal Difference Trading Bots
------------------------------------------------------------------------

    o   Use temporal difference learning to create a trading bot that
        can automatically decide when to buy and sell

    o   Ability to evaluate trading bots against real data
